  <summary date="2021-12-02T19:20:30Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Financing Our Energy Future Act

The bill extends the tax treatment of certain publicly traded partnerships as corporations to renewable and alternative energy projects, transportation fuels, and nuclear-generated electricity facilities. Under current law the tax treatment of such partnerships is only available to investors in energy portfolios for oil, natural gas, coal extraction, and pipeline projects.</summary>
